<h2><strong>Internship / Working Student Customer Experience</strong></h2>
<p><strong>gitti</strong> is a dynamic start-up based in Berlin with a highly skilled team and an outstanding company culture. We are now looking for a <strong>Customer Experience Intern</strong>/working student (m/w/d) who gets excited about supporting and growing our community and creating personalized experiences that will lead to more satisfied and loyal customers.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Your tasks</strong></p>
<p>Support of our Website &amp; Online Shop</p>
<ul>
<li>Maintenance of our website and online shop within Shopify. </li>
<li>Optimization of our online shop with focus on content management, conversion rate and user experience.</li>
<li>Management and optimization of existing processes for our shop management in cooperation with other teams.</li>
</ul>
<p>CRM Management &amp; Email Marketing</p>
<ul>
<li>Supporting the implementation of Marketing- and Sales activities.</li>
<li>Optimization of our E-mail Marketing within Mailchimp – you’ll inspire our community with smart mailings.</li>
<li>Creation of strategic customer segments and individualized email content.</li>
<li>Execution and evaluation of A/B Testing.</li>
<li>Analyzing and optimizing automated campaigns.</li>
