<p>Community Management</p>
<ul>
<li>Managing our customer happiness and representing gitti being in direct contact with our customers via Instagram and our digital customer friendship tool</li>
<li>Identification of our customer’s needs and interests through direct contact, analytics tools and customers surveys created by you.</li>
<li>Development of recommended action for our content creation as well as UX Design to strengthen the relationship with our customers and increase conversion rates.</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Your profile</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>you are a recent graduate or currently pursuing a degree in E-Commerce, Marketing, Communications or related fields.</li>
<li>Previous internships or work experience in a D2C start-up or ecommerce business is a big plus</li>
<li>you love to work with an analytical and creative mindset at the same time, and know how to back up your innovative ideas with relevant data.</li>
<li>You are passionate about relevant content both visually and in written form and are excited to create your own.</li>
<li>You are a digital native and easily dive in to new tools.</li>
<li>You have experience working with e.g. Shopify, Mailchimp or other Analytics and CRM Tools.</li>
<li>you have a good understanding of the most common e-commerce KPIs and feel confident to set up clean a/b testing.</li>
<li>you are service oriented and an empathic communicator with fluent German and excellent English skills.</li>
<li>You have a strong interest in beauty and sustainability as well as observing and identifying trends on various channels.</li>
<li>You love to work in a team and are not shy to present your thoughts and ideas.</li>
